---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home">
  <section class="py-16">
    <h1 class="font-mono text-primary text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold leading-tight mb-6">
      Built from nothing.<br />Earned every rep.<br />Still building.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-text-muted text-lg max-w-2xl mb-10">
      I build red team infrastructure and conduct original security research under the Azrael Security brand.
      My work lives below the abstraction layer; systems, protocols, and the boundaries between them.
    </p>
    <a
      href="/research"
      class="inline-block border border-accent text-accent px-5 py-2 font-mono text-sm hover:bg-accent hover:text-bg transition-colors"
    >
      View Research →
    </a>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-white/10 py-16">
    <h2 class="font-mono text-primary text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Veil</h2>
    <p class="text-text-muted max-w-2xl mb-6">
      Veil is a three-node WireGuard mesh running live red team infrastructure: C2, self-hosted tooling,
      and operator workstations. Built from scratch, operated daily.
    </p>
    <a
      href="/infrastructure"
      class="font-mono text-sm text-accent hover:underline"
    >
      View Infrastructure →
    </a>
  </section>
</Layout>
